=head1 DESCRIPTION

Represents the data payload of an Engagement Invitation for a specific
opportunity. This contains detailed information that partners use to
evaluate the engagement.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Customer => L<Paws::PartnerCentralSelling::EngagementCustomer>

Contains information about the customer related to the opportunity in
the Engagement Invitation. This data helps partners understand the
customerE<rsquo>s profile and requirements.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Project => L<Paws::PartnerCentralSelling::ProjectDetails>

Describes the project details associated with the opportunity,
including the customerE<rsquo>s needs and the scope of work expected to
be performed.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> ReceiverResponsibilities => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

Outlines the responsibilities or expectations of the receiver in the
context of the invitation.


=head2 SenderContacts => ArrayRef[L<Paws::PartnerCentralSelling::SenderContact>]

Represents the contact details of the AWS representatives involved in
sending the Engagement Invitation. These contacts are opportunity
stakeholders.



